                                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                                    <p>
                                                    Similar to single button dropdowns, split button dropdowns can be made by using the same syntax, but with the addition of. For adequate space around the dropdown caret, use <code>dropdown-toggle-split</code>.
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                    Using this additional class, it is possible to eliminate the <code>margin-left</code> that is provided for standard button dropdowns and lower the horizontal padding on each side of the caret by 25%. These additional adjustments retain the caret in the split button's center and create a larger hit area close to the main button.
                                                    </p>

