                                                    <h2 class="mt-20">Events <a href="" id="Events"
                                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                                    <p>All dropdown events are fired at the
                                                        toggling element and then bubbled up. So you can also add event
                                                        listeners on the <code>.dropdown-menu</code>s parent element.
                                                        hide.bs.dropdown and <code>hidden.bs.dropdown</code> events have
                                                        a <code>clickEvent</code> property (only when the original Event
                                                        type is <code>click</code>) that contains an Event Object for
                                                        the click event.</p>

